<div class="fs-main">
    <div class="fs-left">
        <div class="btn fs_btn">
            <div class="play"> </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clip">
            <video id="myvideo" poster="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/5892/9887/files/Video.png?v=1674287411">
                <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/466fb9cc7509481f9fafff7fbb41afc0.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
            <div class="btn vdo_btn">
                <div class="play"> </div>
            </div> <b class="close"><span><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/5892/9887/files/icons8-close-96.png?v=1674297571" alt="close" /></span></b>
        </div>
       <div class="f_img">
        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/5892/9887/files/Jez-img.png?v=1674449718" alt="">
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fs-right">
        <h2>Hi, i’m jez</h2>
        <p class="discription">After spending most of my life as an ultra endurance athlete, extensive knee surgeries left me unable to walk for a year while I recovered</p>
        <p class="discription">Determined to move, I sought to combine the power of an e-skateboard with the design and stability of four wheels. That’s how <strong>Dragonfly — the world's first hyperscooter was created.</strong></p>
        <p class="designation">Jez Williman | CO-Founder</p> <button class="primary">Watch Now</button>
    </div>
</div>

